      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six remains the centerpiece, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis benefits from reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing aluminum control arms. This vehicle maintains its high-revving character and linear power delivery, offering a visceral driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and kinematic precision.",
